{"type": "article", "id": 2218, "title": "复古巧克力包装", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:50:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222255FSiGnI7tgzY2pJyD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">这个世界上很少有人能抗拒黑巧克力的香浓滋味。Lucy Bennetto 也是黑巧克力爱好者之一。她决定深入可可供应链的最前端——位于多米尼亚共和国的种植园去一探究竟，最终她用最原生态的可可粉、原蔗糖再加一点香草制作出了这款黑巧克力块。完全不含人工添加剂和精制砂糖，高达 70% 可可含量，连包装都是用植物墨水印刷，只需一点热牛奶就能冲出这杯史上最健康美味的黑巧克力了。包装上的小鸟是由插画师 Henrietta Harris 特别绘制，为即将到来的秋冬囤点温暖的美味吧。</span><a href=\"http://bennetto.co.nz/#store-stockist\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135050LkZQvnmjP0VWhfcD.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"451\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135052rmKyDG7FPdhX8qkV.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"451\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135053xQnklhfHzmj6Jgsc.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"392\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61298701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135053DQHChwyrgl2Ss8IF.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70364501\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}